SEE ALSO
    LWP::UserAgent::Plugin

    Existing non-plugin solutions: LWP::UserAgent::Determined,
    LWP::UserAgent::ExponentialBackoff.

    Equivalent plugin for HTTP::Tiny::Plugin: HTTP::Tiny::Plugin::Retry

